tathā ca | kusumaśayanīyaṃ puṣpaśayanīyaṃ puṣpaśayyāṃ karoti | kimbhūtaṃ tat | kusumaviśikhaśaratalpamanalpavilāsakalākamanīyam | analpā yā vilāsasya kalāḥ tābhiḥ kamanīyaṃ manoharam | tatkimiva | vratamiva | kasmai | tava parirambhasukhāya | parirambhaṇasyāliṅganasya sukhaṃ tasmai | anyo 'pi yaḥ kaścidabhīṣṭaphalākāṅkṣī bhavati so 'pi duṣkara vratādikaṃ karoti | anena kimuktam | nārāyarṇāvaraha saṃtāpāt kusumaśayanīye 'pi duḥkhaṃ na jahātītyarthaḥ |
